      "source_en": "Consultant synthesis (ASF/ACEA/ACPR)",
      "insight": "고침투·고집중 성숙시장으로 캡티브 장벽이 높다. 진입은 B2B 플릿·중고·구독형 모빌리티 등 틈새 및 파트너십 기반이 현실적.",
      "insight_en": "A high-penetration, high-concentration mature market with high captive barriers. Realistic entry is niche- and partnership-based (B2B fleet, used, subscription mobility).",
      "insight_ai_generated": true,
      "value": "프랑스는 EU 3위 신차시장이자 LOA/LLD 리스 문화가 깊게 자리잡은 시장. Stellantis·Renault 캡티브와 은행계 소비자금융이 지배하며, EV 전환·구독 모빌리티가 신규 성장축. 소비자보호·AI·보험 규제가 강하다.",
      "value_en": "France is the EU's #3 new-car market with deeply rooted LOA/LLD leasing culture. Dominated by Stellantis/Renault captives and bank-affiliated consumer finance, with EV transition and subscription mobility as new growth axes. Consumer-protection, AI, and insurance regulation are strict.",
      "context_type": "descriptive"
    },
